🪪 Step 1: Log in to your personal account

All you need is your email and password, or your QR code if you joined using that method.
Once you’re in, you can post, comment, receive notifications about what matters to you, and more.

Go to Your Profile and click “Edit Profile” to complete your account information.

💬 Step 2: Explore {{network.name}}

Take a look around — browse the posts that are already there, meet other members, and see what people are sharing.

✍️ Step 3: Share something

You can post about anything relevant to your network, such as:

