Remember — a network comes alive when people participate, and you’re part of that movement.

🤝 Step 4: Invite someone else

If you find your network useful, invite a friend, neighbor, or colleague who might also benefit.
You can do this by copying your network’s link, available in the “Invite” section of your dashboard.

Got a question or something isn’t working right?
